name: Jasmine Homestay Darjeeling
description: Jasmine Homestay Darjeeling enjoys a location in Darjeeling, 7.8 miles from Tiger Hill and 5.8 miles from Ghum Monastery. This property offers access to a terrace, free private parking, and free Wifi. The accommodation offers a shuttle service, while a car rental service is also available.

name: Hotel Laxmi Guest House
description: Hotel Laxmi Guest House - Excellent Service is located in Kolkata, within 3.8 miles of Kalighat Kali Temple and 4.9 miles of Indian Museum. This 3-star hotel offers an ATM and a concierge service. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.

name: Grand Inn Lodge
description: GRAND INN LODGE is located in Puri, just 1.5 miles from Golden Beach and 1.5 miles from Puri Beach. This guest house offers air-conditioned accommodations with a balcony. Jagannath Temple is 1.2 miles from the guest house and Konark Sun Temple is 21 miles away.

name: Hotel Paradise
description: Hotel Paradise has accommodations in Mandarmoni. With free WiFi, this 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. There's a restaurant serving Indian cuisine, and free private parking is available.

name: Gitanjali Home
description: Gitanjali Home offers accommodations in Kolkata, 8.7 miles from Dumdum Metro Station and 10 miles from Sealdah Train Station. Among the facilities at this property are an elevator and a shared kitchen, along with free Wifi throughout the property. New Market is 11 miles from the apartment and Howrah Train Station is 11 miles away.
